snippet.title: 『UNDER NIGHT IN-BIRTH II Sys:Celes』Teaser Trailer at EVO2023
snippet.description:
Website: https://www.arcsystemworks.jp/uni2celes

『UNDER NIGHT IN-BIRTH II Sys:Celes』is coming to PS4, PS5, Nintendo Switch and Steam！
Releasing in early 2024！

After 10 years of operation, the 7th title in the series is the first to affix a number!
With completely redesigned visuals, a new tale of Night is depicted. 
Even more playable characters to be added!

The first in the series to include rollback netcode, prepare for blistering online matches.
New moves and new battle systems have been added to further evolve the battle.
Experience high-octane battles with ultra high definition pixel graphics.

The tale of the Hollow Night is about to reach its climax...!

#UN2 #inbirth

© FRENCH-BREAD / ARC SYSTEM WORKS
